snippet.title: Linkin Park - "Papercut" | Haider Ali (Guitar Cover)
snippet.description:
“Papercut” by @Linkin Park from the album Hybrid Theory — released in 2000 under @Warner Records, and produced by Don Gilmore at NRG Recording Studios in North Hollywood, CA, USA — guitar performance by @Haider Ali.

• Subscribe
https://www.youtube.com/haidertonight?sub_confirmation=1

• Thoughts
​I believe that @Linkin Park is one of the most quintessential bands of our time, folks. This song came out at the height of their peak — it has a clear message, and now that Chester is no longer with us, it's hard to listen to this song without feeling Chester's pain (may his soul rest in peace). I am dedicating this cover to Chester. Also, I just want to point out that I did record the lead guitar part, but due to time constraints, I couldn't record the video for it. I hope you guys dig it.
